#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Indledning"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:72
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kontact; is the integrated solution for personal information management. "
#| "It combines the well-known &kde; applications for email, scheduling, "
#| "address book, notes, and newsgroups (&kmail;, &korganizer;, "
#| "&kaddressbook;, &knotes;, and &knode;) into a single interface. Being "
#| "based on a true component framework &kontact; provides exactly the same "
#| "functionality as the stand-alone applications, and adds more features, by "
#| "making use of the integrated way &kontact; runs the applications as "
#| "components. Users still retain the choice of which applications are run "
#| "within &kontact; and which are run stand-alone."
msgid ""
"&kontact; is the integrated solution for personal information management. It "
"combines the well-known &kde; applications for email, scheduling and address "
"book (&kmail;, &korganizer;, &kaddressbook;) into a single interface. Being "
"based on a true component framework &kontact; provides exactly the same "
"functionality as the stand-alone applications, and adds more features, by "
"making use of the integrated way &kontact; runs the applications as "
"components. Users still retain the choice of which applications are run "
"within &kontact; and which are run stand-alone."
msgstr ""
"&kontact; er den integrerede løsning på personlig informationshåndtering. "
"Den kombinerer de velkendte &kde;-programmer for e-mail, kalender, "
"adressebog, noter og nyhedsgrupper (&kmail;, &korganizer;, &kaddressbook;, "
"&knotes; og &knode;) i en enkelt grænseflade. Eftersom det er baseret på et "
"sandt komponentskelet, tilbyder &kontact; nøjagtigt de samme funktioner som "
"de fritstående programmer, og tilføjer flere funktioner ved at udnytte den "
"integrerede måde som &kontact; kører programmerne som komponenter. Brugere "
"beholder stadigvæk valget af hvilke programmer som skal køres i &kontact;, "
"og hvilke som skal køres fritstående."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:80
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "In addition to the functionality of the individual applications &kontact; "
#| "provides, a summary view and advanced drag &amp; drop features between "
#| "components."
msgid ""
"In addition to the functionality of the individual applications, &kontact; "
"provides a summary view and advanced drag &amp; drop features between "
"components."
msgstr ""
"Udover funktionerne i hvert individuelt program sørger &kontact; for en "
"oversigtsvisning og avancerede træk og slip funktioner mellem komponenter."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kontact; Components"
msgstr "Komponenter i &kontact;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kontact; integrates the following applications. See the individual "
"application manuals for details on how to use them. These apply to running "
"them as components inside &kontact; just as well as running them stand-alone."
msgstr ""
"&kontact; integrerer følgende programmer. For detaljer om hvordan de bruges, "
"se hvert programs håndbog. Der beskrives både hvordan de køres som "
"komponenter inde i &kontact;, og hvordan de køres som fritstående programmer."

