#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:278
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "In addition, &kontact; can show a <guilabel>Navigator</guilabel> toolbar, "
#| "which allows you access to the &kontact; components very much like the "
#| "side pane does. However, unlike the side pane, buttons in the "
